    "viz_sec7": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## 7. Threshold Effects\n\nThree non-color effects driven by the same band determination as Threshold colors: **per-band icon swap**, **per-band glow scaling**, and **pulse animation** on the critical/warning band.\n\n### Effect 1 \u2014 Per-band icon swap\n\nEach band can override the icon name. When the band-specific input is non-empty, it replaces the resolved icon after sanitization.\n\n```json\n\"options\": {\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.thresholdIconLow\":  \"error\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.thresholdIconMid\":  \"warning\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.thresholdIconHigh\": \"check_circle\"\n}\n```\n\nThe single largest UX win for status dashboards \u2014 a glance tells you the severity without color interpretation.\n\n### Effect 2 \u2014 Per-band glow scaling\n\nMultiplies the base `glowSize` by a band-specific factor. Set `0` to disable glow entirely for that band.\n\n```json\n\"options\": {\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.glow\": \"yes\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.glowSize\": \"14\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.thresholdGlowScaleLow\":  \"2\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.thresholdGlowScaleMid\":  \"1\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.thresholdGlowScaleHigh\": \"0.6\"\n}\n```\n\nResult: glow doubles in the critical band and shrinks to 60% when healthy.\n\n### Effect 3 \u2014 Pulse animation\n\nAnimates the glow radius via `requestAnimationFrame`. The \"critical\" band auto-tracks direction:\n\n| `thresholdDirection` | Critical band |\n|---|---|\n| `high_good` | Low band (value below `thresholdLow`) |\n| `high_bad` | High band (value at or above `thresholdHigh`) |\n\n```json\n\"options\": {\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.glow\": \"yes\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.thresholdPulse\":      \"critical\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.thresholdPulseSpeed\": \"1.2\"\n}\n```\n\n`thresholdPulse` accepts `no` / `critical` / `warning` / `critical_and_warning`. Pulse requires `glow=yes`.\n\n### Live demo (right column)\n\nThree tiles, **identical configuration**, fed `value` = 25, 70, 95. Watch icon, glow size, and pulse change with the band. The Service Health dashboard (in the app nav) uses the same pattern with real service data.",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "fontSize": "default"
      }
    },
